{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ATTENTION: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Virtual Fighting Championship (VFC)</strong> brings the heart-pounding action of classic fighting games like <i>Street Fighter</i> and <i>Tekken</i> into an immersive VR world. With a perfect balance of realism and over-the-top excitement, VFC delivers a combat experience that rewards real-life skills while making every fight dynamic and engaging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/Clip4GIF.gif?t=1732315593\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you're taking on players from around the world in online matches or perfecting your techniques against a lineup of unique NPC opponents, VFC puts you in control of the action. Each fight is a dynamic, fast-paced showdown where strategy and creativity lead to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easy to pick up but endlessly rewarding to master, VFC offers gameplay for everyone\u2014from casual players looking for fun to competitive fighters aiming for the top. Step into the arena, choose your style, and fight your way in this exciting and highly replayable VR fighting experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/Clip2GIF.gif?t=1732315593\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732315593","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732315593","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732315593","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor